== Overview ==
Server component of android_phonegap_larrys to provide sandwich data   
Data provided includes:   
* meats 
* sandwich choices        
* condiments     
* veggies
* prices
== Dependencies ==

<ul>
<li>perl, DBI, HTTP::Server::Simple <br />
<pre>sudo cpan install "DBI"
sudo cpan install "HTTP::Server::Simple"
sudo cpan install "DBD::SQLite"
</pre>
</li>
<li>sqlite3 <br />
<pre>sudo apt-get install sqlite3</pre>
</li>
</ul>

=== Optional ===

* Web server supporting perl

== Setup and Run ==    
<ol>
<li>Setup the backing database schema and fill with sample data.<br />
<pre>./init.sh</pre>
</li>
<li>Start serving<br />
<pre>./server.pl</pre>
</li>
<li>Test by going to http://localhost:8080/items.pl</li>
<li>Point the android_phonegap_larrys requesting web url to your server.</li>
</ol>
